  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/97ae1d48188169818341832ffa5d5e28.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an Envoy of Death, able to unleash the incredible powers that will make you the most dangerous soul in Limbo. Upgrade your character’s abilities to become the ultimate Soulslinger and take on thrilling challenges in a bloody war against the criminal cartel of the afterlife!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/67858710eba72b9453f47eff62cb0c46.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the rich and immersive world of Haven, filled with mysterious NPCs who hold the secrets to its dark history. Be wary of the allies and enemies you make as every encounter might shape your journey ahead. In this mesmerizing western-fantasy world, you will experience a tale of grief, loss, and one man's obsession with cheating death itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/26e57178dd634e04faf5200869f487c7.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your own destiny with every run by crafting powerful weapons and unlocking permanent upgrades in Haven. Grow stronger with every new challenge and become an incredibly deadly gunslinger. Get ready for a fast-paced rogue-lite FPS experience you won’t ever forget!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/bee8576f5bf33395b6e5d938d004a914.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced, story-driven roguelike FPS set in random sequences of rooms built in a unique western-fantasy world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Soulslinger through a deep upgrade system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a tightly written story filled with loyal allies and charismatic villains. The story adapts to what you do in the roguelike gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of gun fodder creeps that attack in waves, spiced up by challenging elite mobs</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/97ae1d48188169818341832ffa5d5e28.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/fd32632cfacfe81dff343f42f449d701.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an Envoy of Death, able to unleash the incredible powers that will make you the most dangerous soul in Limbo. Upgrade your character’s abilities to become the ultimate Soulslinger and take on thrilling challenges in a bloody war against the criminal cartel of the afterlife!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/67858710eba72b9453f47eff62cb0c46.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/5b3d706e8602f094a90170eb5ac37305.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the rich and immersive world of Haven, filled with mysterious NPCs who hold the secrets to its dark history. Be wary of the allies and enemies you make as every encounter might shape your journey ahead. In this mesmerizing western-fantasy world, you will experience a tale of grief, loss, and one man's obsession with cheating death itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/26e57178dd634e04faf5200869f487c7.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.poster.avif?t=1764867788\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.webm?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/24fc1d4fcecb87b3ddb2ded1b80edb93.mp4?t=1764867788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your own destiny with every run by crafting powerful weapons and unlocking permanent upgrades in Haven. Grow stronger with every new challenge and become an incredibly deadly gunslinger. Get ready for a fast-paced rogue-lite FPS experience you won’t ever forget!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p